<Layout title="How Brisbane Property Valuations Work: What Moves the Number Up or Down | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Bank valuation vs agent appraisal, the comparable sales method, and the five factors Brisbane valuers weight most heavily. What every Brisbane homeowner needs to know before listing." schema={faqSchema}>

